column2: "Oh my, what's this this you say?! You want to become even stronger as a Ranger?!"
"This is good! This is good, you know? Okay, alright! Lisa will set something up for you."
"Okay! Please go and obliterate these assigned enemies, you know?"
"Lisa takes no responsibility if you die, you know? Go give it everything you've got! Except your life. Don't give that. You would die if you did that, you know?"
"Okay! Bye bye! Good news or bad news, your headline or your obituary; Lisa will be looking forward to whatever report you bring her!"
